HEADWORD: Superhuman
<hw>Su`per*hu"man</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Above or beyond
what is human; sometimes, divine; <as>as, <ex>superhuman</ex> strength;
<ex>superhuman</ex> wisdom</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

